# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in a real key to make the site's
# forms (the Chapter 08 waitlist and the /contact enquiry form) actually
# send. Get a free access key at https://web3forms.com — no backend, no
# account on our side, nothing to host.
#
# Until this is set, both forms still validate and demo their full flow,
# but honestly report "not yet connected" instead of pretending to send.

NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
